---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer | Dongho Lee Real Estate"
  description="Website disclaimer for Dongho Lee Real Estate."
>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <header>
      <p class="page-kicker">Disclaimer</p>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: July 18, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <section>
        <h2>General Website Information</h2>
        <p>
          The information on this website is provided for general informational purposes only. It should not be treated as professional legal, financial, tax, mortgage, appraisal, or investment advice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Real Estate Market Information</h2>
        <p>
          Market commentary, statistics, and blog posts are based on available information and interpretation at the time of publication. Real estate conditions can change quickly, and figures may vary by source, property type, location, and date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>No Guarantee Of Outcome</h2>
        <p>
          Past market performance, example scenarios, or general guidance do not guarantee future results. Buying, selling, renting, and investing decisions involve risk and should be assessed based on your own goals and circumstances.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>External Links</h2>
        <p>
          This website may link to third-party websites or resources. Those links are provided for convenience only, and we are not responsible for external website content, availability, privacy practices, or accuracy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Representation And RECO Information</h2>
        <p>
          Website use, a download, an open-house registration, or an inquiry does not create a representation
          relationship. Before providing real estate services or assistance, the applicable RECO consumer
          information must be provided and explained and the nature of the relationship clarified.
          See <a href="/consumer-information/">RECO Consumer Information</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Remuneration, Commission And HST</h2>
        <p>
          Real estate remuneration and commission are not fixed by law and may be negotiable. Any remuneration,
          payment responsibility, applicable HST, services, and referral arrangements will be disclosed and
          documented in the applicable written agreement. Website examples are not a quote or promise of fees.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>
          Before making a real estate decision, consult the appropriate professionals, including a lawyer, mortgage professional, accountant, inspector, or other advisor as needed.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
